{"title":"小鸟的歌〔越南民歌〕","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔越南民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高山上鲜花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻姑娘把花采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采花泡水洗长发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前有只小鸟唱起来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水滋润着大树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡伯伯比泉水更美；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲哺育着孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡伯伯比母亲的乳汁更珍贵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡伯伯保卫着人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比树根更牢不可摧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡伯伯的胸怀啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比日月更加光辉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘洗长发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发着芳香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟心里喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更纵声欢唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（李子明译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}